## Changes

### 1. Move TransactionService + shared models into `aitbc` package

**Status**: Done (prior session).

**Problem:** `TransactionService` (Ed25519 signing, balance/nonce queries, signed transaction generation) lived in the Hermes service at `apps/hermes/src/hermes_service/services/transaction_service.py`. The Agent Coordinator already duplicated some of this logic inline in `agent_stream.py` (`_generate_signed_transaction`, `_submit_transaction`). The CLI `coin-requests execute` command imported `TransactionService` and `CoinRequest`/`get_db_session` directly from `hermes_service.*` — a fragile cross-app internal import. Having two implementations of transaction signing is error-prone (the v0.5.8 fee mismatch was partly caused by this split).

**Fix:** Moved `TransactionService`, `CoinRequest` model, `CoinRequestStatus` enum, and `get_db_session`/`init_db` into the shared `aitbc` package so both the Agent Coordinator and CLI import from there — no cross-app internal imports.

**Shared package structure:**
```
aitbc/
├── crypto/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   └── transaction_service.py    # TransactionService (moved from hermes_service.services)
├── models/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   └── coin_request.py           # CoinRequest, CoinRequestStatus (moved from hermes_service.storage)
└── db/
    ├── __init__.py
    └── hermes_db.py               # get_db_session, init_db (moved from hermes_service.storage)
```

**Files created:**
- `aitbc/crypto/transaction_service.py` — `TransactionService` (moved from `hermes_service.services.transaction_service`)
- `aitbc/models/coin_request.py` — `CoinRequest`, `CoinRequestStatus` (moved from `hermes_service.storage.schema`)
- `aitbc/db/hermes_db.py` — `get_db_session`, `init_db` (moved from `hermes_service.storage.database`)
- `aitbc/models/__init__.py` — package init exporting `Base`, `CoinRequest`, `CoinRequestStatus`
- `aitbc/db/__init__.py` — package init exporting `get_db_session`, `init_db`, `get_db_path`

**Files updated:**
- `aitbc/crypto/__init__.py` — added `from .transaction_service import TransactionService` and `"TransactionService"` to `__all__`
- `apps/agent-coordinator/src/app/websocket/agent_stream.py` — replaced inline `_generate_signed_transaction` with `from aitbc.crypto import TransactionService`

**Env vars:** `BLOCKCHAIN_RPC_URL`, `CHAIN_ID`, `GENESIS_PRIVATE_KEY`, `GENESIS_ADDRESS` — already available to Agent Coordinator via `/etc/aitbc/blockchain.env` and `blockchain-secrets.env`

